en_139592_0	Money allowances will not be given to Provincial Councils that do not adhere by the ‘Nearest school- the best school’ project’, Minister of Education Akila Viraj Kariyawasam said.
en_139592_1	He made this comment during the opening of a three story building at the U. B. Wanninayake National School in Galgamuwa.
en_139592_2	He also added that retired school teachers will be hired as a temporary solution to teacher shortage.
